      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VARAZZE (10) is a 19-start maiden but looks a great chance to finally get the monkey off her back. Raced on the speed but couldn't run a strong 1405m on a heavy track last start at Coffs Harbour. Has placed six times at this trip and loves racing here. Should be fine in these conditions over the shorter trip so give her one last chance. MARKWELL TOPSORT (3) lines up for the third time after two close seconds to launch his career, both times over 800m at Coffs on rain-affected tracks. Goes fast and only has to run a strong 1000m to be right in the finish. Unbackable at the early prices on offer though. SWEET MARLENE (9) lines up for the 20th time. Has raced here at this trip three times for three placings so she must be respected. The first starters JUSTBEYOURSELF (2) and EXPENSIVE ICON (1) haven't set the world on fire at the trials but in a thin race a podium finish for either is not out of the question.",
